Skill.Name: Ground State Calibration
Skill.Desc:
<size=40><color=Title>Basic Attack</color></size>
Perform up to 3 consecutive attacks, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.
Release the <color=Highlight>Normal Attack</color> button within a certain time after <color=Highlight>Basic Attack Stage 3</color> to automatically cast <color=Highlight>Basic Attack Stage 4</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Heavy Attack</color></size>
Consume STA to attack the target, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode</color></size>
While in <color=Highlight><te href=120902>Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode</te></color>, <color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color> is replaced with <color=Highlight>Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode</color>.
Perform up to 3 consecutive attacks, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>. 
Can be performed in mid-air.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Mid-air Attack</color></size>
Consume STA to perform Mid-air Plunging Attack, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>. {Cus:Ipt,Touch=Tap PC=Press Gamepad=Press} <color=Highlight>Normal Attack</color> within a certain time afterward to cast <color=Highlight>Basic Attack Stage 3</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Dodge Counter</color></size>
{Cus:Ipt,Touch=Tap PC=Press Gamepad=Press} <color=Highlight>Normal Attack</color> right after a successful <color=Highlight>Dodge</color> to attack the target, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.
{Cus:Ipt,Touch=Tap PC=Press Gamepad=Press} <color=Highlight>Normal Attack</color> shortly after performing this attack to perform <color=Highlight>Basic Attack Stage 2</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Dodge Counter - Wide Field Observation Mode</color></size>
While in <color=Highlight><te href=120902>Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode</te></color>, <color=Highlight>Dodge Counter</color> is replaced with <color=Highlight>Dodge Counter - Wide Field Observation Mode</color>.
{Cus:Ipt,Touch=Tap PC=Press Gamepad=Press} <color=Highlight>Normal Attack</color> right after a successful <color=Highlight>Dodge</color> to perform <color=Highlight>Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode Stage 2</color>.
Skill.SimpleDesc:
<size=40><color=Title>Basic Attack</color></size>
Deal <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Heavy Attack</color></size>
Consume STA to deal <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Mid-air Attack</color></size>
Consume STA to perform Mid-air Plunging Attack, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Dodge Counter</color></size>
{Cus:Ipt,Touch=Tap PC=Press Gamepad=Press} <color=Highlight>Normal Attack</color> right after a successful <color=Highlight>Dodge</color> to attack the target, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.

Skill.Name: Resolution
Skill.Desc:
<size=40><color=Title>Resonance Skill - Expectation Error</color></size>
Heal all nearby Resonators in the team and enter the Parry state. Switching to another Resonator ends this mode immediately.
If attacked while in the Parry state, automatically trigger <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Optimal Solution</color>, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color> and resetting the cooldown of <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Expectation Error</color>. Damage taken from the triggering attack is reduced by 100%.
If no attack is taken during the Parry state, {Cus:Ipt,Touch=tap PC=press Gamepad=press} <color=Highlight>Normal Attack</color> shortly after to perform <color=Highlight>Basic Attack Stage 2</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Resonance Skill - Distributed Array</color></size>
While in <color=Highlight><te href=120902>Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode</te></color>, Resonance Skill is replaced with <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Distributed Array</color>.
Heal all nearby Resonators in the team and summon Hover Cannons to strike the target, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.
Can be performed in mid-air.
Skill.SimpleDesc:
<size=40><color=Title>Ground Resonance Skill</color></size>
Heal all nearby Resonators and enter a parry state. Upon a successful parry, performs a counterattack on the target and resets the cooldown of <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill  Expectation Error</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Mid-air Resonance Skill</color></size>
While in <color=Highlight>Hovering Mode</color>, Resonance Skill is replaced with <color=Highlight>Mid-air Resonance Skill</color>.
Heal all nearby Resonators in the team and deal <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.

Skill.Name: Critical Protocol
Skill.Desc:
Attack all targets within the effective range, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.
For every {1} of Mornye's Energy Regen exceeding {0}, this skill gains an additional {2} Crit. Rate (up to {3}) and {4} Crit. DMG (up to {5}).
When casting this skill, if a <color=Highlight><te href=120907>Syntony Field</te></color> is present, remove it and generate a <color=Highlight><te href=120908>High Syntony Field</te></color>.
Can be performed in mid-air.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>High Syntony Field</color></size>
- <color=Highlight>High Syntony Field</color> lasts for {6}s. 
- Increases the DEF of all nearby Resonators in the team within the <color=Highlight>High Syntony Field</color> by {8}.
- Inherits the <color=Highlight><te href=120907>Syntony Field</te></color>'s boost to resistance to interruption and <color=Highlight>Off-Tune Buildup Rate</color>.
- Inherits the <color=Highlight><te href=120907>Syntony Field</te></color>'s healing effect and increases the Healing Multiplier by {7}.
Skill.SimpleDesc:
Deal <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.
Mornye's excessive Energy Regen increases this skill's Crit. Rate and Crit. DMG.
Casting this skill destroy any existing <color=Highlight>Field</color> and generates a <color=Highlight>Enhanced Field</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Enhanced Field</color></size>
- Lasts for {6}s.
- Continuously restores HP for the active Resonator.
- All nearby Resonators in the team gain DEF and <color=Highlight>Off-Tune Buildup Rate</color> increase and enhanced resistance to interruption.

Skill.Name: Blueprint
Skill.Desc:
Mornye's Energy Regen is increased by {4}.
Casting <color=Highlight>Intro Skill</color> restores {0} points of Concerto Energy, triggered once every {1}s.
Casting <color=Highlight>Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode Stage 3</color> restores {2} points of Concerto Energy, triggered once every {3}s.
Skill.SimpleDesc: Mornye's Energy Regen increases. Casting <color=Highlight>Intro Skill</color> or <color=Highlight>Basic Attack Stage 3</color> in mid-air restores Concerto Energy.

Skill.Name: Boundedness
Skill.Desc:
Casting <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Expectation Error</color> or <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Distributed Array</color> grants <color=Highlight>Proof of Boundedness</color> to all Resonators in the team:
- <color=Highlight>Proof of Boundedness</color> lasts for {0}s and can be gained once every {1} min.
- When the active Resonator takes DMG greater than {2} of their Max HP, they instead take DMG equal to {3} of their Max HP. This effect can trigger up to <SapTag=4>{4}</SapTag> {Cus:Sap,S=time P=times SapTag=4}. <color=Highlight>Proof of Boundedness</color> is removed after triggering it <SapTag=5>{5}</SapTag> {Cus:Sap,S=time P=times SapTag=5}.
- When the active Resonator takes a fatal blow, they are not downed by this instance of damage. This effect can trigger up to <SapTag=6>{6}</SapTag> {Cus:Sap,S=time P=times SapTag=6}. <color=Highlight>Proof of Boundedness</color> is removed after triggering it <SapTag=7>{7}</SapTag> {Cus:Sap,S=time P=times SapTag=7}.
- When <color=Highlight>Proof of Boundedness</color> is removed, the active Resonator restores HP equal to {8} of Mornye's DEF.
Skill.SimpleDesc: Casting <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill/color> grants <color=Highlight>Proof of Boundedness</color> to all Resonators in the team, reducing incoming DMG and preventing one instance of fatal damage within a certain time.

Skill.Name: Convergence
Skill.Desc: Attack the target to deal <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>, clearing all <color=Highlight><te href=120903>Rest Mass Energy</te></color> and entering <color=Highlight><te href=120902>Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode</te></color>.

Skill.Name: Mass-Energy Equivalence
Skill.Desc:
<size=40><color=Title>Baseline Mode</color></size>
While in her default <color=Highlight>Baseline Mode</color>, Mornye gains <color=Highlight><te href=120903>Rest Mass Energy</te></color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Heavy Attack - Geopotential Shift</color></size>
When <color=Highlight><te href=120903>Rest Mass Energy</te></color> reaches {0} points, Heavy Attack is replaced with <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Geopotential Shift</color>.
Consume all <color=Highlight><te href=120903>Rest Mass Energy</te></color> to cast <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Geopotential Shift</color>, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>, considered Heavy Attack DMG. Afterward, jump into mid-air and enter <color=Highlight><te href=120902>Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode</te></color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Wide Field Observation Mode</color></size>
<color=Highlight>Wide Field Observation Mode</color> last for {11}s.
- Upon entering <color=Highlight>Wide Field Observation Mode</color>, Mornye generates a <color=Highlight><te href=120907>Syntony Field</te></color>.
- While in <color=Highlight>Wide Field Observation Mode</color>, Mornye gains <color=Highlight><te href=120904>Relative Momentum</te></color>.
- If <color=Highlight><te href=120904>Relative Momentum</te></color> is below {0} when holding <color=Highlight>Normal Attack</color>, perform <color=Highlight>Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode Stage 1 to 3</color> in sequence. If <color=Highlight><te href=120904>Relative Momentum</te></color> reaches {0} during this time, cast <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Inversion</color> instead.
- When Mornye is hit or launched into mid-air, {Cus:Ipt,Touch=tap PC=press Gamepad=press} Dodge to immediatelty recover from the attack. This effect can be triggered up to {12} times. The triggering count resets when <color=Highlight>Wide Field Observation Mode</color> ends.
- <color=Highlight>Wide Field Observation Mode</color> ends upon landing after being launched.
Performing environmental interactions, using Utilities, switching to another Resonator, or {Cus:Ipt,Touch=tapping PC=pressing Gamepad=pressing} Jump and landing on the ground will end the <color=Highlight>Wide Field Observation Mode</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Syntony Field</color></size>
- <color=Highlight>Syntony Field</color> lasts for {1}s.
- When the <color=Highlight>Syntony Field</color> is generated, all targets within its effective range take <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>, considered Resonance Liberation DMG.
- Continuously restores HP for all nearby Resonators in the team within the <color=Highlight>Syntony Field</color>, triggered once every {2}s.
- Increases the <color=Highlight>Off-Tune Buildup Rate</color> of all nearby Resonators in the team within the <color=Highlight>Syntony Field</color> by {3}.
- Enhances the resistance to interruption of all nearby Resonators in the team within the <color=Highlight>Syntony Field</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Heavy Attack - Inversion</color></size>
- When <color=Highlight><te href=120904>Relative Momentum</te></color> reaches {0} points, Heavy Attack is replaced with <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Inversion</color>.
- Consume all <color=Highlight><te href=120904>Relative Momentum</te></color> to cast <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Inversion</color>, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>, considered Heavy Attack DMG.
- <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Inversion</color> inflicts <color=Highlight><te href=120905>Observation Marker</te></color> upon the target on hit for {4}s.
Can be performed in mid-air.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Observation Marker</color></size>
When a Resonator in the team deals <color=Highlight><te href=100001>Tune Break</te></color> DMG to a target inflicted with <color=Highlight>Observation Marker</color>, and that target is also affected by <color=Highlight><te href=100002>Tune Rupture - Shifting</te></color> or <color=Highlight><te href=100003>Tune Strain - Shifting</te></color>, Mornye inflicts an <color=Highlight><te href=120906>Interfered Marker</te></color> on the target for {5}s.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Interfered Marker</color></size>
Targets with <color=Highlight>Interfered Marker</color> take increased DMG from all nearby Resonators in the team. For every {8} of Mornye's Energy Regen exceeding {7}, she deals {9} more DMG, up to {10}.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Visual Field</color></size>
When a Resonator in the team defeats a target inflicted with <color=Highlight><te href=120905>Observation Marker</te></color> or <color=Highlight><te href=120906>Interfered Marker</te></color>, Mornye gains <color=Highlight>Visual Field</color> for {6}s. While in this state, Mornye inflicts <color=Highlight><te href=120905>Observation Marker</te></color> on the target hit whenever any Resonator in the team deals damage.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Tune Rupture Response - Particle Jet</color></size>
Mornye deals one instance of <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color> to a targets in the <color=Highlight><te href=100004>Tune Rupture - Interfered</te></color> state within range, considered <color=Highlight>Tune Rupture DMG</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Rest Mass Energy</color></size>
Mornye can hold up to {0} points of <color=Highlight>Rest Mass Energy</color>.
While in <color=Highlight><te href=120901>Baseline Mode</te></color>, she gains <color=Highlight>Rest Mass Energy</color> when performing <color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color>, <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack</color>, <color=Highlight>Dodge Counter</color>, or when <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Optimal Solution</color> hits a target.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Relative Momentum</color></size>
Mornye can hold up to {0} points of <color=Highlight>Relative Momentum</color>.
While in <color=Highlight><te href=120902>Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode</te></color>, she gains <color=Highlight>Relative Momentum</color> when <color=Highlight>Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode</color> or <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Distributed Array</color> hits the target.
Mornye cannot gain <color=Highlight>Relative Momentum</color> during <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Inversion</color>.
Skill.SimpleDesc:
<size=40><color=Title>Forte Gauge</color></size>
Mornye gains <color=Highlight>Ground Mode Energy</color> while on the ground, and <color=Highlight>Hovering Mode Energy</color> while in the air.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Enhanced Ground Heavy Attack</color></size>
With full <color=Highlight>Ground Mode Energy</color>, <color=Highlight>Enhanced Ground Heavy Attack</color> becomes available.
Consume all <color=Highlight>Ground Mode Energy</color> to cast <color=Highlight>Enhanced Ground Heavy Attack</color>, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>. Afterward, enter <color=Highlight>Hovering Mode</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Hovering Mode</color></size>
<color=Highlight>Hovering Mode</color> lasts for {11}s.
- Upon entering this mode, generate a <color=Highlight>Field</color>, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Field</color></size>
- <color=Highlight>Field</color> lasts for {1}s.
- Continuously restores HP for all nearby Resonators in the team.
- Increases the <color=Highlight>Off-Tune Buildup Rate</color> and resistance to interruption of all nearby Resonators in the team.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Enhanced Mid-air Heavy Attack</color></size>
With full <color=Highlight>Hovering Mode Energy</color>, <color=Highlight>Enhanced Mid-air Heavy Attack</color> becomes available.
Consume all <color=Highlight>Hovering Mode Energy</color> to cast <color=Highlight>Enhanced Heavy Attack</color>, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color> and <color=Highlight>Mark</color> the target for {4}s.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Marker</color></size>
When a <color=Highlight>Marked</color> in target takes any damage via <color=Highlight>Tune Break</color>, if that target is also affected by <color=Highlight>Tune Rupture - Shifting</color> or <color=Highlight>Tune Strain - Shifting</color>, Mornye inflicts an <color=Highlight>Enhanced Marker</color> on the target for {5}s.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Enhanced Marker</color></size>
All nearby Resonators in the team deal more DMG to target with <color=Highlight>Enhanced Marker</color>.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Visual Field</color></size>
When a target inflicted with <color=Highlight>Marker</color> or <color=Highlight>Enhanced Marker</color> is defeated, within a certain period of time, Mornye <color=Highlight>Marks</color> the target hit whenever a Resonator in the team deals damage.
<size=10></size>
<size=40><color=Title>Tune Rupture Response - Particle Jet</color></size>
Deal <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>, considered <color=Highlight>Tune Rupture DMG</color>.

30.Name: Tune Rupture Response - Particle Jet DMG

Skill.Name: Recursion
Skill.Desc: All Resonators in the team gain {0} All-Type DMG Amplification for {1}s.
Skill.SimpleDesc: All Resonators in the team gain All-Type DMG Amplification for {1}s.

Skill.Name: Decoupling
Skill.Desc:
Mornye can respond to <color=Highlight><te href=100004>Tune Rupture - Interfered</te></color> and <color=Highlight><te href=100005>Tune Strain - Interfered</te></color>.
Responding to <color=Highlight><te href=100004>Tune Rupture - Interfered</te></color>: When the active Resonator deals damage to a target affected by <color=Highlight><te href=100004>Tune Rupture - Interfered</te></color>, Mornye casts <color=Highlight>Tune Rupture Response - Particle Jet</color>. Each target can be damaged by this skill up to once every {0}s.
Responding to <color=Highlight><te href=100005>Tune Strain - Interfered</te></color>: Each stack of <color=Highlight><te href=100005>Tune Strain - Interfered</te></color> on the target increases Mornye's total DMG against them. Every point of Mornye's <color=Highlight>Tune Break Boost</color> increases the total DMG by {1}. While Mornye is in the team, the max stack limit of <color=Highlight><te href=100005>Tune Strain - Interfered</te></color> on a target is increased by {2}.
Mornye can perform <color=Highlight><te href=100001>Tune Break</te></color> against the targets with full <color=Highlight>Off-Tune Level</color>.
Skill.SimpleDesc: Mornye can respond to Tune Rupture - Interfered and Tune Strain - Interfered. Mornye can perform Tune Break against the targets with full Off-Tune Level.

1.Name: The Silent Observer
1.Desc:
<color=Highlight>Basic Attack  Wide Field Observation Mode</color> becomes immune to interruption.
Mornye can now inflict <color=Highlight><te href=120906>Interfered Marker</te></color> even when the target is not affected by <color=Highlight><te href=100002>Tune Rupture - Shifting</te></color> or <color=Highlight><te href=100003>Tune Strain - Shifting</te></color>. Interfered Marker's duration is extended by {0}s.
When Mornye applies <color=Highlight><te href=120905>Observation Marker</te></color> on a target, she also inflicts <color=Highlight>Interfered Marker</color>.

2.Name: Morning Star of Entropy
2.Desc:
All nearby Resonators in the team gain Crit. DMG increase against targets with <color=Highlight><te href=120906>Interfered Marker</te></color>: Every {2} of Mornye's Energy Regen over {1} grants {3} Crit. DMG increase, up to {4}.
<color=Highlight><te href=120907>Syntony Field</te></color> and <color=Highlight><te href=120908>High Syntony Field</te></color> further increase the <color=Highlight>Off-Tune Buildup Rate</color> of all Resonators in the team by {0}.

3.Name: Blueprint of Recursion
3.Desc: Casting <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Distributed Array</color> additionally restores {0} points of Concerto Energy and all <color=Highlight><te href=120904>Relative Momentum</te></color>, triggered once every {1}s.

4.Name: Latent Variables of the Cosmos
4.Desc: The healing of <color=Highlight><te href=120908>High Syntony Field</te></color> is increased by {0}.

5.Name: Time Dilation Effect
5.Desc:
The DMG Multiplier of <color=Highlight>Resonance Liberation - Critical Protocol</color> is increased by {0}.
The DMG Multiplier of <color=Highlight>Tune Rupture Response - Particle Jet</color>is increased by {1}.

6.Name: To the Far Shores of the Stars
6.Desc: <color=Highlight>Resonance Liberation - Critical Protocol</color> deals {0} more DMG. If Mornye has not engaged in combat for over {1}s, she restores Resonance Energy equal to {2} of her Max Resonance Energy every {4}s.

81001209.Name: Mornye
81001209.BgDescription:
A standard uniform of the Spacetrek Collective Research Institute.
Wearing it, the petite girl moves among data streams, machinery, and shifting currents. Beneath the silent gaze of the stars, humanity's drive to explore never ceases.
